{"ts":"2026-07-05T05:09:03.180Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-4a7m"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Promote history-stream maintenance primitives to the public SDK: history-redact, history-repair, history-compact (audited rewrite, re-anchor, checkpoint/prune)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"The existing promotion set (pm-98cz lifecycle, pm-rjqr reads, pm-zwpp facets, pm-oxrw governance, pm-3mna workspace config) leaves the history MUTATION family uncovered: history-redact (audited redaction), history-repair (chain re-anchor after drift), history-compact (checkpoint/prune preserving replay integrity), all built on the shared history-rewrite orchestration (dedup'd in closed pm-bzgt). SDK-first requires these as public typed primitives so the consolidated pm history subcommands (pm-tqel) become thin shims and integrators can run stream maintenance programmatically. Duplicate check: pm-tqel is the CLI-grammar counterpart; pm-xk39/pm-bzgt closed history; no open SDK-promotion overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["architecture","area:history","area:sdk"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-05T05:09:03.180Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-05T05:09:03.180Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":240},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"SDK exports typed redact/repair/compact primitives preserving audited-rewrite guarantees (hash chain continuity, replay integrity, checkpoint markers, redaction audit trail) and returning the same structured results the CLI prints; CLI history maintenance commands consume only these primitives; docstrings + linked tests + SDK reference docs; zero behavior change (history rewrite/compact/redact specs green)."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-usfg"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-lodl","kind":"blocked_by","created_at":"2026-07-05T05:09:03.180Z"},{"id":"pm-muhw","kind":"blocked_by","created_at":"2026-07-05T05:09:03.180Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"bffe12a195bce87cc6397312a5f75090ee361ad7526816bb5555e123765b6a58","message":""}
{"ts":"2026-07-10T17:46:11.524Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-10T17:46:11.524Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-10T17:46:11.520Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Promotion slicing S1-S4 (pass #53 code survey). Territory = history-redact.ts 783 + history-compact.ts 759 + history-repair.ts 428 lines; ALL domain logic (rule parsing, rewrite, replay, re-anchor, rollback) lives in CLI command files; SDK exports none of it. Blockers pm-lodl/pm-muhw closed - actionable now.\nDuplication evidence: applyHistoryPatch is implemented TWICE (history-redact.ts:313 and history-compact.ts:169) inside command files while core/history/replay.ts exists - promotion consolidates into one kernel.\nS1 redaction engine (~90m): move buildRedactionRules / applyLiteralRule / applyRegexRule / redactUnknownValue / rewriteHistoryEntries / inspectHistoryIntegrity + apply/rollback into core/history/redaction.ts; SDK exports redactHistory() returning the audit-trail result (rules applied, replacement counts, integrity snapshot).\nS2 repair primitive (~45m): history-repair.ts (428 lines, 6 fns) becomes repairHistory() re-anchor primitive taking a drift report from scanHistoryDrift.\nS3 compact primitive (~75m): parseBeforeBoundary / replayHistoryAndResolveCheckpoint / reanchorRetainedEntries / apply-rewrite become compactHistory() checkpoint/prune primitive; core/history/history-compact-bulk.ts is already core-side - align with it.\nS4 shared integrity kernel (~60m): one replay + hash-chain verification module consumed by all three primitives AND by the immutability consumers pm-3z0k (attestation) and pm-hib1 (get --at) - same kernel, multiple call sites; replay-integrity spec matrix + SDK reference docs.\nRecommended entry: S1 (largest file, fully self-contained pure functions); fold the kernel extraction into whichever of S1/S3 lands first."}]}],"before_hash":"bffe12a195bce87cc6397312a5f75090ee361ad7526816bb5555e123765b6a58","after_hash":"0120aaeda4f77194321ff2b4c90b8d5301a589d27f9e471d14e924c3636efad8"}
